**Workflow:**
User -> Planner;
Planner -> WebSearcher;
WebSearcher -> Validator;
Validator -> Summarizer;
Summarizer -> End.

**Description:**
1. Planner creates a search strategy with explicit verification milestones
2. WebSearcher executes targeted searches using precise Wikipedia terminology
3. Validator cross-checks nomination details across three sources (nomination archive, talk page history, featured log)
4. Summarizer constructs a validated answer with timestamp alignment
